Package: AccumulatR
Type: Package
Title: Native Likelihood Kernels for Race Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Niek", "Stevenson", email = "niek.stevenson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides R and C++ tools for building simulators and
    likelihood functions for generalized race models. Users prepare a
    model once in R, obtain a serialized native context plus per-trial
    metadata, and then execute likelihood evaluations on the C++ side.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    Rcpp,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    DiagrammeR
LinkingTo: Rcpp, BH
SystemRequirements: C++17
NeedsCompilation: yes
LazyData: false
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
